headline: At Trane Technologies, the CEO’s Focus on Sustainability Also Applies to Financials
summary: Dave Regnery has run  Trane Technologies  a maker of heating, ventilation, and air-conditioning equipment, since 2021.  Trane shares have returned an impressive 25% annually during his tenure, well ahead of the  10.3% return in the same span.  A focus on sustainability has helped.
